  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle, then take your<strong> chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and slice into thin strips</p><p>Slice your<strong> chestnut mushrooms </strong>finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger </strong>and <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Admin10mm-Step-1-1642072780864-x200.jpg",
