        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>diced chicken breast </strong>and cook for<strong> </strong>7-8 min or until browned</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
