    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> medium egg noodles nest</strong> to a pot of<strong> boiling water</strong> over a high heat and cook for 5-7 min or until the noodles are cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain, reserving a cup of <strong>starchy noodle water</strong> then return to the pot</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
