    {
      "instruction": "<p>Melt 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>butter</strong> in a small bowl in the <strong>microwave </strong>for 20 secs (gently heat in a pot if you don't have a microwave!)</p><p>Once melted, add your<strong> soy sauce</strong>, <strong>white miso paste</strong>, a pinch of<strong> sugar </strong>and the <strong>chopped ginger </strong>and<strong> garlic</strong> and whisk to combine – this is your<strong> miso-butter</strong></p>",
