    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is almost cooked, add the<strong> pepper strips</strong>, <strong>sliced mushrooms</strong> and <strong>mangetout</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min or until the veg is slightly softened but still crunchy and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
